en.name: ANA Tactical M2 plate carrier (MultiCam Alpine)
en.description: The M2 vest is created with the use of the best experience of Russian special forces operators. The versatility of the system makes it possible to use this vest both when carrying out urban tasks and when performing tasks on rough terrain. Manufactured by ANA Tactical. MultiCam Alpine version.

weaponpresets._name: Vest ANA Tactical M2 Alpine Standard

en.name: Tac-Kek JayPC plate carrier (OD Green)
en.description: A cheap airsoft bootleg of the Crye Precision JPC plate carrier. Doesn't offer the comfort of the original JPC, but retains extensive customization options. Someone attached an IOTV shoulder pad to this one to act as a groin protector.

weaponpresets._name: Vest Crye Precision JPC Wild_02 Standart

en.name: Tac-Kek JayPC plate carrier (Black)
en.description: A cheap airsoft bootleg of the Crye Precision JPC plate carrier. Doesn't offer the comfort of the original JPC, but retains extensive customization options. It looks like the previous owner chose not to overload the carrier with pouches to stay as mobile as possible.

weaponpresets._name: Vest Crye Precision JPC Wild_01 Standart

en.name: Crye Precision JPC Plate Carrier (MultiCam)
en.description: The widely beloved Jumpable Plate Carrier (JPC) was designed to maximize operator mobility by reducing weight and bulk. Its modular system allows for personalized loadouts and quick gear adjustments depending on the mission. Manufactured by Crye Precision. MultiCam version.

weaponpresets._name: Vest Crye Precision JPC MilSpec Standart
